@startuml sequence_overview
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #555
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderColor #AAAAAA

title Agent Pipeline — Overview\nPOST /api/chat  (happy path)

actor   "User"          as User
box "FastAPI :8000" #F5F5F5
  participant "API"     as API
end box
box "LangGraph Workflow" #EBF5FB
  participant "intake_node\n[A1]"     as A1 #BBDEFB
  participant "retrieval_node\n[A2]"  as A2 #C8E6C9
  participant "planning_node\n[A3]"   as A3 #FFF9C4
  participant "validator_node\n[A4]"  as A4 #FFCCBC
  participant "response_node\n[A5]"   as A5 #E1BEE7
end box

User  ->  API : POST /api/chat\n{ message, top_k, with_plan }
API   ->  A1  : invoke(state)

A1    ->  A1  : LLM extract intent\n(temp=0.0)

alt intake incomplete
  A1  --> API : follow_up_questions
  API --> User : "Missing: destination/days/interests"
else intake complete
  A1  ->  A2  : collected_info { destination,\n  days, interests, budget, companion }

  A2  ->  A2  : embed → Chroma search\n+ weather fetch
  A2  ->  A3  : places[20], weather

  A3  ->  A3  : load DB pool → VRP/LLM plan\n+ budget-aware hotel scoring\n+ TrackAsia routing
  A3  ->  A4  : plan, route_plan, hotel

  A4  ->  A4  : LLM validate + distance check
  alt validation failed
    A4  ->  A3  : needs_replan=True
    A3  ->  A4  : revised plan (retry ×1)
  end

  A4  ->  A5  : plan_validation { passed: true }
  A5  ->  A5  : format_planning_answer()
  A5  --> API : response_payload
  API --> User : ChatResponse\n{ answer, plan, route_plan,\n  hotel, validation, timings }
end

note over User, A5
  Typical latency breakdown:
  A1 ~1s  |  A2 ~2s  |  A3 ~10s  |  A4 ~4s  |  A5 <0.5s
  Total: ~17s  (retry adds +10s, occurs ~80% of queries)
end note

@enduml
